ğŸ§  Application Server (e.g., Gunicorn, uWSGI, Node.js)
â€¢	Role: Executes dynamic business logic, processes requests, handles database interaction via the app codebase.
â€¢	Why Separate: Application logic can scale independently, isolates security and performance bottlenecks.
